      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It's heartbreaking to see the immense investment and time you've dedicated to your research suddenly feeling futile. Recognize that exhaustion and demotivation can set in, especially when faced with defeat. Remind yourself that identity is not tied solely to your research or lab, and that you have skills and passions worth exploring. Allow yourself to grieve the loss, but also consider new paths and possibilities where you can reignite your spark.",
