    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "the problem is that \"taking a step back\" or \"relaxing\" doesn't actually make the noise stop. i'm still here, still thinking about everything i failed at, still feeling the weight of it all every second. it's not a break if the thoughts follow you. i just want a rest that actually works. a rest that's permanent and quiet. like, i just want to be finished with all of this once and for all.",
